---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Casa de Mercaderias"
  description="Camiseta Imperial y suscripciones de Imperio Espanol."
>
  <main class="storefront">
    <section class="store-catalog" id="catalogo">
      <header class="store-header">
        <a class="store-mark" href="/" aria-label="Volver al inicio" title="Volver al inicio">
          <img src="/images/logo-redv2.png" alt="" width="64" height="54" />
        </a>

        <nav class="store-nav" aria-label="Navegacion de la tienda">
          <a href="#mercancias">Mercancias</a>
          <a href="#suscripciones">Suscripciones</a>
        </nav>

        <a class="store-account" href="/cuenta">Cuenta</a>
      </header>

      <div class="catalog-heading">
        <p>Casa de Mercaderias</p>
        <h1>TIENDA</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="catalog-toolbar" id="mercancias">
        <div class="catalog-filters" aria-label="Filtrar productos">
          <button class="filter-button is-active" type="button" data-filter="all">
            Todo <sup>3</sup>
          </button>
          <button class="filter-button" type="button" data-filter="indumentaria">
            Indumentaria
          </button>
          <button class="filter-button" type="button" data-filter="suscripcion">
            Suscripciones
          </button>
        </div>

        <label class="catalog-search">
          <span class="sr-only">Buscar en la tienda</span>
          <input
            type="search"
            placeholder="Buscar por producto o categoria"
            autocomplete="off"
            data-product-search
          />
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid" data-product-grid>
        <article
          class="product-card product-card--shirt"
          data-category="indumentaria"
          data-search="camiseta imperial indumentaria ropa"
          id="camiseta"
        >
          <div class="product-meta">
            <span>Indumentaria</span>
            <strong>CAMISETA IMPERIAL</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="product-visual product-visual--placeholder">
            <img src="/images/logo-redv2.png" alt="" width="180" height="153" />
          </div>
          <div class="product-purchase">
            <p class="product-price">29,99 EUR</p>
            <label class="size-field">
              <span>Talla</span>
              <select data-shirt-size>
                <option value="S">S</option>
                <option value="M" selected>M</option>
                <option value="L">L</option>
                <option value="XL">XL</option>
              </select>
            </label>
            <button
              class="store-button store-button--light"
              type="button"
              data-product="camiseta-imperial"
            >
              Comprar
            </button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article
          class="product-card"
          data-category="suscripcion"
          data-search="arcabucero suscripcion mensual archivo"
        >
          <div class="product-meta">
            <span>Suscripcion</span>
            <strong>ARCABUCERO</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="product-visual product-visual--tier">
            <span>03</span>
            <p>Archivo completo<br />y cronicas premium</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product-purchase">
            <p class="product-price">3 EUR / mes</p>
            <button
              class="store-button store-button--light"
              type="button"
              data-plan="arcabucero-monthly"
            >
              Suscribirme
            </button>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article
          class="product-card"
          data-category="suscripcion"
          data-search="maestre de campo suscripcion mensual ventajas"
        >
          <div class="product-meta">
            <span>Suscripcion</span>
            <strong>MAESTRE DE CAMPO</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="product-visual product-visual--tier product-visual--tier-red">
            <span>06</span>
            <p>Acceso superior<br />y ventajas reservadas</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product-purchase">
            <p class="product-price">6 EUR / mes</p>
            <button
              class="store-button store-button--light"
              type="button"
              data-plan="maestre-campo-monthly"
            >
              Suscribirme
            </button>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <p class="catalog-empty" data-catalog-empty hidden>No hay productos con ese criterio.</p>
      <p class="checkout-status" data-checkout-status role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
    </section>

    <section class="subscription-story" id="suscripciones">
      <h2>SUSCRIPCIONES</h2>

      <div class="subscription-columns">
        <article>
          <span>01 / Piquero</span>
          <p>
            La entrada gratuita a Imperio Espanol. Incluye el manifiesto, una seleccion
            de lecturas y la gaceta basica para seguir el pulso del proyecto.
          </p>
          <a href="/registro">Crear cuenta</a>
        </article>
        <article>
          <span>02 / Arcabucero</span>
          <p>
            Abre el archivo completo, las cronicas premium y las rutas de lectura.
            Una suscripcion mensual para sostener la publicacion.
          </p>
          <button type="button" data-plan="arcabucero-monthly">Elegir Arcabucero</button>
        </article>
        <article>
          <span>03 / Maestre de Campo</span>
          <p>
            El acceso superior a la comunidad, con ventajas reservadas, prioridad
            editorial y el archivo completo de Imperio Espanol.
          </p>
          <button type="button" data-plan="maestre-campo-monthly">
            Elegir Maestre de Campo
          </button>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="subscription-illustration" aria-hidden="true">
        <img
          src="/images/ejercito-blanco_upscaled_2x.webp"
          alt=""
          width="1900"
          height="1267"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  const filterButtons = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll("[data-filter]"));
  const productCards = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll("[data-category]"));
  const searchInput = document.querySelector("[data-product-search]");
  const emptyState = document.querySelector("[data-catalog-empty]");
  const status = document.querySelector("[data-checkout-status]");
  let activeFilter = "all";

  function updateProducts() {
    const query =
      searchInput instanceof HTMLInputElement
        ? searchInput.value.trim().toLocaleLowerCase("es")
        : "";
    let visibleCount = 0;

    productCards.forEach((card) => {
      if (!(card instanceof HTMLElement)) return;

      const matchesFilter =
        activeFilter === "all" || card.dataset.category === activeFilter;
      const matchesSearch = (card.dataset.search || "").includes(query);
      const isVisible = matchesFilter && matchesSearch;

      card.hidden = !isVisible;
      if (isVisible) visibleCount += 1;
    });

    if (emptyState instanceof HTMLElement) {
      emptyState.hidden = visibleCount !== 0;
    }
  }

  filterButtons.forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener("click", () => {
      activeFilter = button.getAttribute("data-filter") || "all";
      filterButtons.forEach((item) => item.classList.toggle("is-active", item === button));
      updateProducts();
    });
  });

  searchInput?.addEventListener("input", updateProducts);

  function setStatus(message) {
    if (status) status.textContent = message;
  }

  async function openCheckout(button, payload) {
    if (!(button instanceof HTMLButtonElement)) return;

    const originalText = button.textContent || "Continuar";
    button.disabled = true;
    button.textContent = "Abriendo Stripe...";
    setStatus("");

    try {
      const response = await fetch("/api/create-checkout-session", {
        method: "POST",
        headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" },
        body: JSON.stringify(payload),
      });
      const data = await response.json().catch(() => ({}));

      if (response.ok && data.url) {
        window.location.href = data.url;
        return;
      }

      setStatus(data.error || "No se pudo iniciar el pago.");
    } catch (error) {
      console.error(error);
      setStatus("No se pudo iniciar el pago.");
    } finally {
      button.disabled = false;
      button.textContent = originalText;
    }
  }

  document.querySelectorAll("button[data-plan]").forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener("click", () => {
      openCheckout(button, { plan: button.getAttribute("data-plan") });
    });
  });

  document.querySelectorAll("button[data-product]").forEach((button) => {
    button.addEventListener("click", () => {
      const card = button.closest(".product-card");
      const sizeField = card?.querySelector("[data-shirt-size]");
      const size = sizeField instanceof HTMLSelectElement ? sizeField.value : "";

      openCheckout(button, {
        product: button.getAttribute("data-product"),
        size,
      });
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  :global(body) {
    background: #0a0a0a;
  }

  :global(#imperio-scrollbar-track) {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .storefront {
    padding: 0;
    color: #f7f7f4;
    background: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .store-catalog {
    min-height: 94svh;
    padding: 0 clamp(1.25rem, 4.2vw, 5rem) clamp(5rem, 8vw, 9rem);
    background: #0a0a0a;
  }

  .store-header {
    min-height: 84px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #2b2b2b;
  }

  .store-mark {
    width: 58px;
    justify-self: start;
  }

  .store-mark img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    filter: grayscale(1) brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .store-nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 3.5rem);
    color: #8c8c8c;
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .store-nav a,
  .store-account {
    transition: color 180ms ease;
  }

  .store-nav a:hover,
  .store-account:hover {
    color: #f23b20;
  }

  .store-account {
    justify-self: end;
    color: #f7f7f4;
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .catalog-heading {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.65fr) minmax(0, 2.35fr);
    align-items: end;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 8rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
  }

  .catalog-heading p {
    margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
    color: #7d7d7d;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .catalog-heading h1 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #f7f7f4;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 0.76;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .catalog-toolbar {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.65fr) minmax(0, 2.35fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 6rem);
  }

  .catalog-filters {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.7rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .filter-button {
    padding: 0;
    border: 0;
    color: #6e6e6e;
    background: transparent;
    font: 500 0.9rem/1.4 var(--font-body);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .filter-button sup {
    color: #f23b20;
  }

  .filter-button.is-active {
    color: #f23b20;
  }

  .catalog-search input {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 64px;
    padding: 0 1.4rem;
    border: 1px solid #242424;
    border-radius: 6px;
    outline: none;
    color: #f7f7f4;
    background: #171717;
    font: 500 0.92rem/1 var(--font-body);
  }

  .catalog-search input:focus {
    border-color: #f23b20;
  }

  .catalog-search input::placeholder {
    color: #747474;
  }

  .product-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 2rem);
  }

  .product-card {
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .product-card[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .product-meta {
    min-height: 58px;
    display: grid;
    align-content: end;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .product-meta span {
    color: #6f6f6f;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }

  .product-meta strong {
    color: #f7f7f4;
    font: 600 clamp(0.88rem, 1.25vw, 1.12rem)/1.25 var(--font-body);
  }

  .product-visual {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #1c1c1c;
  }

  .product-visual--placeholder {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: #efefeb;
  }

  .product-visual--placeholder img {
    width: min(40%, 180px);
    height: auto;
  }

  .product-visual--tier {
    display: grid;
    align-content: space-between;
    padding: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    color: #f7f7f4;
    background: #202020;
  }

  .product-visual--tier-red {
    background: #8e1117;
  }

  .product-visual--tier > span {
    font: 500 clamp(5rem, 10vw, 10rem)/0.8 var(--font-display);
  }

  .product-visual--tier p {
    margin: 0;
    color: inherit;
    font: 600 clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.35rem)/1.25 var(--font-body);
  }

  .product-purchase {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: end;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .product-price {
    margin: 0;
    color: #f7f7f4;
    font: 600 0.95rem/1.3 var(--font-body);
  }

  .size-field {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    grid-column: 1;
    color: #8b8b8b;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
  }

  .size-field select {
    min-width: 64px;
    min-height: 40px;
    border: 1px solid #3a3a3a;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #f7f7f4;
    background: #171717;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .store-button {
    min-height: 42px;
    padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font: 600 0.82rem/1 var(--font-body);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .store-button--light {
    grid-column: 2;
    grid-row: 1 / span 2;
    color: #0a0a0a;
    background: #f7f7f4;
  }

  .store-button:disabled {
    cursor: wait;
    opacity: 0.62;
  }

  .catalog-empty,
  .checkout-status {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
    color: #a6a6a6;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .subscription-story {
    min-height: 100svh;
    padding: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 8rem) clamp(1.25rem, 4.2vw, 5rem) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: #fff;
    background: #f2381e;
  }

  .subscription-story h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 9vw, 10rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 0.86;
    letter-spacing: 0;
  }

  .subscription-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 7rem);
    padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 8rem) 0 clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }

  .subscription-columns article {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
  }

  .subscription-columns span {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .subscription-columns p {
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.15vw, 1.05rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .subscription-columns a,
  .subscription-columns button {
    width: fit-content;
    padding: 0 0 0.3rem;
    border: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;
    color: #fff;
    background: transparent;
    font: 700 0.82rem/1.2 var(--font-body);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .subscription-illustration {
    height: clamp(250px, 42vw, 650px);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0;
    background: #111;
  }

  .subscription-illustration img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 58%;
  }

  .sr-only {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .product-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .subscription-columns {
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .store-header {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      min-height: 72px;
    }

    .store-mark {
      width: 48px;
    }

    .store-nav {
      display: none;
    }

    .catalog-heading,
    .catalog-toolbar {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .catalog-heading {
      padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    }

    .catalog-heading h1 {
      font-size: clamp(3.7rem, 23vw, 6rem);
    }

    .catalog-search input {
      min-height: 56px;
    }

    .product-grid,
    .subscription-columns {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
    }

    .product-meta {
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .product-visual {
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.12;
    }

    .subscription-story h2 {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 16vw, 5.5rem);
    }

    .subscription-columns {
      padding-top: 4rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .store-nav a,
    .store-account {
      transition: none;
    }
  }
</style>
